    "Both ORGAN and ORGANIC rely heavily on SMILES strings and, therefore, suffer from the same issue of 100% validated SMILES that plagues most seq2seq models.",
    "GANs' training and performance might be erratic and sluggish.",
    "Furthermore, training and convergence for GANs are often more challenging.",
    "Additionally, for optimal performance, hyperparameters must frequently be finetuned.",
    "As mentioned earlier, another issue is mode collapse, which is theoretically impossible to prevent (Su, 2018)."
